Extract metadata

Description

Parameters

  • Extractor mode
    • Type: ChoiceP
    • Default value: Filename
    • Choices:
      • Filename
      • Foldername
      • Keyword
      • Metadata file
  • Filename extractor
    • Type: ChoiceP
    • Default value: Generic
    • Choices:
      • Generic
      • Cell Voyager filename
      • IncuCyte long filename
      • IncuCyte short filename
      • Opera filename
      • Yokogawa filename
  • Foldername extractor
    • Type: ChoiceP
    • Default value: None
    • Choices:
      • None
      • Cell Voyager foldername
      • Opera measurement foldername
      • Opera barcode
  • Pattern
    • Type: StringP
  • Groups (comma separated)
    • Type: StringP
  • Show pattern matching test
    • Type: BooleanP
    • Default value: false
  • Example string
    • Type: StringP
  • Identified groups
    • Type: TextDisplayP
  • Keyword list
    • Type: StringP
  • Keyword source
    • Type: ChoiceP
    • Default value: File name
    • Choices:
      • File name
      • Series name
  • Metadata file extractor
    • Type: ChoiceP
    • Default value: None
    • Choices:
      • None
      • CSV file
      • Opera file (.flex)
  • Input source
    • Type: ChoiceP
    • Default value: File in input folder
    • Choices:
      • File in input folder
      • Static file
  • Metadata file
    • Type: FilePathP
  • Metadata file name
    • Type: StringP
  • Metadata item to match
    • Type: MetadataItemP
